claim: Rachel McAdams was in the drama Perfect Pie.
premise_source_doc_sentence: After graduating from a four-year theatre program at York University in 2001 , she initially worked in Canadian television and film productions such as the drama film Perfect Pie  (  2002  )   (  for which she received a Genie Award nomination  )  , the comedy film My Name Is Tanino  (  2002  )  , and the comedy series Slings and Arrows  (  for which she won a Gemini Award  )  .
